haust-their-devils\/","url_meta":{"origin":38472,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: Believers exhaust their devils by obeying Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the believer will wear down his devils by obedience to Allah, just as one of you wears down his camel on a journey.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 8717 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40611,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/04\/shaytan-plays-bells\/","url_meta":{"origin":38472,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Bells: Satan plays his music with bells","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe bell is an instrument of Satan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2114 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 2114 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d \u0645\u0633\u0644\u0645 \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0628\u0627\u0633\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37109,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/12\/bismillah-before-toilet\/","url_meta":{"origin":38472,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Bathrooms: Bismillah before entering the toilet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 12, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA screen will be placed between the eyes of the Jinn and the nakedness of the children of Adam if one of them says as he enters the washroom: In the name of Allah.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39259,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/03\/18\/shaytan-is-pleased\/","url_meta":{"origin":38472,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Wrongdoing: Satan is pleased when Muslims oppress each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Satan has despaired that idols will be worshipped in the land of the Arabs, but rather he will be pleased with you for less than that by your contempt for each other, which is a punishment\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15930,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/09\/05\/salat-al-jamaah-fard-kifayah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38472,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Community: Devil attacks the isolated sheep","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported:\u00a0The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf three people in a town or in the desert do not establish prayer among them, then Satan has overcome them. You must establish the congregation, for the wolf eats the isolated\u00a0sheep.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 547 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34101,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/06\/allah-loves-concessions\/","url_meta":{"origin":38472,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Rukhsa: Allah loves believers taking His concessions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah loves for you to take His concessions, just as He loves you to fulfill His edicts.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 354 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u202